## 📋 critical file checklist

| file/directory | purpose | action if missing |
|----------------|---------|-------------------|
| `memory-bank/` | core directory for all memory bank files | create directory |
| `memory-bank/tasks.md` | tracks all tasks and their status | create file |
| `memory-bank/activecontext.md` | holds current focus and context | create file |
| `memory-bank/progress.md` | logs progress and key events | create file |
| `memory-bank/projectbrief.md` | contains project overview | create file |
| `memory-bank/productcontext.md` | details product context | create file |
| `memory-bank/systempatterns.md` | documents system patterns | create file |
| `memory-bank/techcontext.md` | describes technical context | create file |
| `.cursorrules` | defines cursor ide rules | create file |

## 🔄 file creation process

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant verifier as file verifier
    participant filesystem as file system
    
    verifier->>filesystem: check for memory-bank/
    filesystem-->>verifier: not found
    verifier->>filesystem: create memory-bank/
    
    verifier->>filesystem: check for tasks.md
    filesystem-->>verifier: not found
    verifier->>filesystem: create tasks.md
    
    verifier->>filesystem: check for activecontext.md
    filesystem-->>verifier: not found
    verifier->>filesystem: create activecontext.md
    
    verifier->>verifier: repeat for all critical files
```

